Description: Codon usage tables
        ===================
        
        For Python 3+
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        via pip:
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            pip install codon_usage_tables
        
        Manual:
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            (sudo) python setup.py develop
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        
        .. code:: python
        
            import codon_usage_tables
        
            # PRINT THE NAMES OF ALL AVAILABLE TABLES
            print (codon_usage_tables.available_tables)
        
            # LOAD ONE TABLE BY NAME
            table = codon_usage_tables.get_table("b_subtilis_1423")
            print (table['T']['ACA'])  # returns 0.4
            print (table['*']['UAA'])  # returns 0.61
        
        
            # LOAD ALL TABLES AT ONCE
            codon_tables = codon_usage_tables.get_all_tables()
            print (table['c_elegans_6239']['L']['CUA'])  # returns 0.09
        
Keywords: DNA codon usage
